{
  "name": "FTC-WF-004_forum-registro",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## FTC-WF-004 | Forum Registro\n**Descripcion:** Flujo de registro de asistentes al Chile Fintech Forum 2026. Recibe datos de Typeform/Tally, verifica membresia y sponsorship en Notion, crea registro de evento, envia confirmacion por email, crea invitacion en Google Calendar y notifica en Slack.\n\n**Owner:** MBC Operator / FinteChile Ops\n**Fecha de creacion:** 2026-02-18\n**Version:** 1.0.0\n**Folder:** /Eventos\n**Criticidad:** Alta\n\n**Variables de entorno requeridas:**\n- `NOTION_DB_EMPRESAS_ID`\n- `NOTION_DB_EVENTOS_ID`\n- `NOTION_DB_SPONSORS_ID`\n- `SLACK_CHANNEL_OPS`\n- `EMAIL_FROM`",
        "height": 380,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "sticky-metadata",
      "name": "Metadata WF-004",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -200,
        -100
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "ftc-wf-004-forum-registro",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {
          "responseContentType": "application/json"
        }
      },
      "id": "webhook-trigger",
      "name": "Webhook: Registro Forum",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        300,
        300
      ],
      "webhookId": "ftc-wf-004-forum-registro"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Validate and normalize incoming registration data\nconst body = $input.item.json.body;\n\nconst nombre = (body.nombre || '').trim();\nconst email = (body.email || '').trim().toLowerCase();\nconst empresa = (body.empresa || '').trim();\nconst cargo = (body.cargo || '').trim();\nconst telefono = (body.telefono || '').trim();\nconst tipo_ticket = (body.tipo_ticket || 'General').trim();\nconst es_socio = body.es_socio === true || body.es_socio === 'true' || body.es_socio === 1;\n\n// Validation\nconst errors = [];\nif (!nombre) errors.push('nombre es requerido');\nif (!email) errors.push('email es requerido');\nif (!empresa) errors.push('empresa es requerido');\nif (email && !/^[^\\s@]+@[^\\s@]+\\.[^\\s@]+$/.test(email)) {\n  errors.push('email no es valido');\n}\n\nif (errors.length > 0) {\n  throw new Error(`Datos de registro invalidos: ${errors.join(', ')}`);\n}\n\n// Generate confirmation number\nconst timestamp = Date.now().toString(36).toUpperCase();\nconst randomPart = Math.random().toString(36).substring(2, 6).toUpperCase();\nconst confirmationNumber = `FTF26-${timestamp}-${randomPart}`;\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    nombre,\n    email,\n    empresa,\n    cargo,\n    telefono,\n    tipo_ticket,\n    es_socio,\n    confirmation_number: confirmationNumber,\n    registration_date: new Date().toISOString(),\n    event_name: 'Chile Fintech Forum 2026',\n    event_date: '2026-06-15',\n    event_time_start: '09:00',\n    event_time_end: '18:00',\n    event_location: 'Santiago, Chile'\n  }\n};"
      },
      "id": "code-validate",
      "name": "Validar y Normalizar Datos",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        520,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "databasePage",
        "operation": "getAll",
        "databaseId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "id",
